{"tid":1641549,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"創立: HKGoldenHuman 首個去中化(無大台)模式企業","createTime":"2019-10-09T11:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T22:36:33.000Z","uid":198071,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b315ab4bb29b03770dede4ef25ee111b75114cab","tid":1641549,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"HKGoldenHuman 運作模式完全公開，以去中化(無大台)方式經營，這是首個去中化模式企業。 HKGoldenHuman 利用Sansor的VIRTUAL WORLD技術， 創造IELTS英文交流區。這個平台最主要是用於英語訓練，大家可以在這裏扮演會話考試的考官以及學生，虛擬世界有大量屋以及郊區讓大家找地方練習英語。而且可以用Oculus rift進入虛擬世界。所有的管理是完全公開，<span style=\"color: red;\">不會有眾籌</span>，未來所有的本地顧客以及員工可以選出CEO。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>HKGoldenHuman未來目標:</strong><br />\n<br />\n1)未來目標令鍵盤戰士可以在由居民組成的專門市場，同一些實體公司合作做網店或把虛擬財產兌換成美元。現在先行利用免費的Sansor server(全球最大的Virtual world server,假如有錢再自行研發), 再建一個虛擬香港。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如何進入虛擬世界?</strong><br />\n<br />\n1)先到Sansor  download SansarInstaller.exe<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sansar.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sansar.com&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNrAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=185a9848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sansar.com</a><br />\n<br />\n2) 之後用EMAIL登記帳號，選擇自己的角色。<br />\n<br />\n3) 選擇左邊Menu的第一個選項<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFg8Dp3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFg8Dp3.png&h=b5139d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 之後選擇Codex<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9RwBbK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9RwBbK.png&h=a5b5ee78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5)之後尋找HkGoldenHuman<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZ6D0Dq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZ6D0Dq.png&h=1956808e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBjunRM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBjunRM.png&h=8edd2bf6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5)之後載入畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJBc449.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJBc449.png&h=a7a969e5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1zSr9wT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1zSr9wT.png&h=a2b29aba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d5a2a64701c61bb7911fd168f681ecba6ae4006","tid":1641549,"uid":198071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"英語討論需要帶耳機，利用麥克風進行對話否則會有回音。"},{"pid":"227d64b97a95410931ac824a5d06fd626cccb134","tid":1641549,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0633459b75a0a576e7c739922577e73e586bd0e","tid":1641549,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d92b8e00a49c39d51858e05bd5c1a6ee6b100c","tid":1641549,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:21:04.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"ca569103a9d4cf644bfdf99e42099beadf7c13c9","tid":1641549,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:21:31.000Z","msg":"租金不是問題"},{"pid":"fa54b7a7d41be4de1d69ab58964deefbac4ead4f","tid":1641549,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177efc28a7d085310f6a25a4948a68c9c4524350","tid":1641549,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:22:38.000Z","msg":"召喚IELTS巴絲"},{"pid":"1922629942bc6682c4f416ddf2d1dfe8f8296134","tid":1641549,"uid":2607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"改錯名"},{"pid":"69349b3ffa18bf5f71284c5d0754b95cac8df500","tid":1641549,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT